<div style="font-size:90%">
<br><br>

<b>2012 September 08  Visitors from Tokyo's Seiwa Kai aikido group</b><br><br><br>

A delegation from Tokyo's Seiwa Kai group will make their annual visit to the Philippines, with their customary stopover at the Makati Aikido Club. The group will train with the regular Saturday class at Makati Sports. Leading the visitors group are Makoto Hayashi Sensei (6th dan), Mr. Susumu Shoji Sensei (6th dan), and Mr. Tadashi Nishiyama Sensei (4th dan).<br><br>

